comments:
build M-20021023 (2.0.2)

- opened an existing workspace created with 2.1 using the 2.0.2 build
- after some time, I noticed that opening editors and using the context menu in 
the packages view was very slow, both taking several seconds
- in the log there was the following (all of these stacks are within two 
seconds of each other)
- there were many more entries like this, some of which were on the CVS/Entries 
file rather than the CVS/Root file
- did a refresh on the package in question; this did not fix the problem
- did a refresh on the project; this fixed it

Not sure if it was the switch from 2.1 to 2.0.2 that caused this, or something 
else.
